<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/MM_AW_014.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>

  <ol id="questionList">
    <li id="1">Stories in the media about famous people often cause&#xA0; <input id="q1" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;distress.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="2">Governments should avoid taking measures&#xA0; <input id="q2" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;limit the freedom of the press.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="3">Politicians who behave badly, whether in public or in private, should not be surprised if they find&#xA0; <input id="q3" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;the object of media attention.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="4">Politicians&#xA0; <input id="q4" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;families are the objects of unwanted media attention have every right to complain.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="5">Public figures&#xA0; <input id="q5" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;lead discreet lives should be free from press harassment.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="6">The fact that there are a large number of gossip magazines reporting on the private lives of the rich and famous is proof that there is a market for&#xA0; <input id="q6" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;stories.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="7">Trivial stories about the rich and famous often attract more media attention than more important&#xA0; <input id="q7" type="droptarget"/>.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="8">Writing about famous people' s private lives does not serve the public interest.&#xA0; <input id="q8" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;just a way to increase sales.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="9">The press could not perform&#xA0; <input id="q9" type="droptarget"/> &#xA0;role properly if the government imposed too many restrictions on journalists.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
    <li id="10">Some public figures encourage the media to report on their private lives when it suits&#xA0; <input id="q10" type="droptarget"/>.</li>
	<p class="linespace"></p>
  </ol>
</section>

